race.comment: AMAZING CHEAT (4) won impressively two back before another strong victory last start, running over the top to score at this track and trip. She can sit closer this time around and the sectionals she ran to win last start were very impressive. Hitting her straps now and can extend her winning run. AUDIO BOY (8) stuck on well over 1.8L over 1800m here two back before just missing behind AMAZING CHEAT last start when the race favourite. Drawn awkwardly, but possesses some early speed and there's no reason why he can't turn the tables. PONY UP (11) is a 3YO filly on the way up. She stuck on well at her first try over 2200m last start and will be better for that effort. She can roll forward from the sticky draw and with no weight on her back, she'll be very hard to run down. STARWALKER (12) was put into the race last start in what looked a targeted assault. Wasn't beaten far though and commands respect. KISSES FROM KELLY (3) is in the mix on recent efforts.
